{"type":"message","id":"bd481725","parentId":"19926c06","timestamp":"2026-04-16T00:00:00.919Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[cron:da4546e3-8bdd-4291-b88f-472a4b5d4b34 盘前-MyQuant选股] 执行盘前 MyQuant 选股：\n1. 先检查今天是否交易日（2026年休市日：20260101 20260102 20260216-20260220 20260223 20260406 20260501 20260504 20260505 20260619 20260925 20261001-20261007），休市则输出\"休市\"结束\n2. 运行: cd /Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant && /opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin/python -m myquant preopen > /tmp/preopen_$(date +%Y%m%d).log 2>&1\n3. 等待完成（约2分钟，Tushare调用较多），检查 outputs/preopen/YYYYMMDD/ 下 top_y5.csv 是否存在且是新生成的（检查文件修改时间）\n4. 如果成功，输出\"preopen 完成，候选池 N 只\"；如果失败，输出错误信息\nCurrent time: Thursday, April 16th, 2026 — 08:00 (Asia/Shanghai) / 2026-04-16 00:00 UTC\n\nReturn your summary as plain text; it will be delivered automatically. If the task explicitly calls for messaging a specific external recipient, note who/where it should go instead of sending it yourself."}],"timestamp":1776297600918}}
{"type":"message","id":"a94b1b6a","parentId":"bd481725","timestamp":"2026-04-16T00:00:24.082Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"\n用户发送了一个 cron 任务的执行指令，看起来是 MyQuant 量化交易系统的盘前选股任务。我需要按照指令的要求执行：\n\n1. 检查今天是否是交易日（2026年休市日已经给出）\n2. 运行 MyQuant 的 preopen 命令\n3. 检查输出文件是否存在且是新生成的\n4. 返回执行结果\n\n让我先检查今天是几号，然后在检查是否为交易日。\n\n今天是2026年4月16日，查看休市日列表：\n- 20260101 20260102 \n- 20260216-20260220 (这包括了2月16-20日)\n- 20260223 \n- 20260406 \n- 20260501 20260504 20260505 \n- 20260619 \n- 20260925 \n- 2026010-20260107 (10月1-7日)\n\n2026年4月16日不在休市日列表中，所以今天是交易日。\n\n然后我需要执行命令：\n```bash\ncd /Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant && /opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin/python -m myquant preopen > /tmp/preopen_$(date +%Y%m%d).log 2>&1\n```\n\n等待完成后检查 outputs/preopen/20260416/ 目录下的 top_y5.csv 文件。\n\n让我执行这个任务。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"\n我将执行这个 MyQuant 盘前选股任务。首先检查今天是交易日，然后运行选股命令。\n"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_32d032e58f8f44c5abfd7dd5","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"cd /Users/lynch/Codes/MyQuant && /opt/miniconda3/envs/MyQuant/bin/python -m myquant preopen > /tmp/preopen_$(date +%Y%m%d).log 2>&1","yieldMs":120000}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"custom-customb2","model":"glm-5-turbo","usage":{"input":37203,"output":414,"cacheRead":5268,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":42885,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1776297600919,"responseId":"20260416080002bea857e6b5f54e39"}}
